#: ../../C/control-S.rst:5
msgid "control-S"
msgstr "control-S"

#: ../../C/control-S.rst:7
msgid "vi\\."
msgstr "自動詞"

#: ../../C/control-S.rst:9
msgid ""
"\"Stop talking for a second.\" From the ASCII DC3 or XOFF character (the "
"pronunciation /X-of/ is therefore also used). Control-S differs from "
":ref:`control-O` in that the person is asked to stop talking (perhaps "
"because you are on the phone) but will be allowed to continue when you're "
"ready to listen to him — as opposed to control-O, which has more of the "
"meaning of \"Shut up.\" Considered silly."
msgstr ""
"「ちょっとしゃべるのをやめて」。ASCII DC3またはXOFF文字から(したがって発音/X-of/も使われます)。Control-Sが\\ "
":ref:`control-O`\\ "
"と異なるのは、(たぶんあなたが電話中だからという理由で)その人にしゃべるのをやめるよう頼むが、あなたが聞く準備ができたら続けてよいという点です——「黙れ」という意味合いがより強いcontrol-"
"Oとは対照的です。おどけたものとみなされます。"
